3.4

  @{b}Automatic play-through (HIDDEN SPECIAL FUNCTION):@{ub}

By push-and-hold with the mouse on the 'Next/last move', and move the mouse
up above the icon before the button is released, an automatic play-through
starts. Higher gives faster (upto mid of the window). It stops by the end of
game, or by executing a new command.

       NOTE: not always working from v2.7

